=======
 This check monitors all AWS EBS and reports a summary of their states.

 It monitors:

 - The amount of stores

 - The amount of stores for each state

 - The amount of stores for each type

 - Name of volume, status, type, encryption and creation time for each store

>>>>>>> upstream/master
 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

